name: Kernel gt-s5830c
body:
Samsung Galaxy ACE
Model: GT-S5830C-i-M
CPU: Broadcom 21553 ARM11
Arquitecture: ARM1136JF-S


This Kernel version 2.6.35.7 is compiled from Samsung sources, with GCC 4.4.7 compiled from sources,
specific to arm1136jf-s.
I changed in sources for add more frequencies to cpu and configured to add features.
The kernel can be used on any rom.


### Install dependencies
$ ./install_dep.sh

### Configure and Compile
$ ./Compile.sh
